cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper deals with deep learning models for object detection and semantic segmentation, which are both subfields of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the challenges of training a multitask model, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on real-time deployment suggests a potential application in robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the use of deep learning models implies a connection to neural networks (cs.NE).
